{"tid":760052,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"廢撚咗1000蚊紙佢啦","createTime":"2018-07-29T07:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T13:04:38.000Z","uid":19386,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd8daa87dc89675204e63cfa6642bc47bb2bc34","tid":760052,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"正話食飯，食4百幾蚊，1000蚊紙唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後去7-11，去增值300蚊，都話冇得找，屌你老母咁大間7仔連2張1001張500都冇？<br />\n<br />\n邊度都唔收，咁1000蚊紙要嚟做咩？我又唔係俾1000蚊買支水，1000蚊買幾舊水既野都好合理<br />\n<br />\n你話唔收邊年邊個版既1000蚊紙都算啦，度度都寫「千元紙幣怒不接受」，係咪on撚9？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2118bbaa3a1766ebe18826d0669a6d727e887525","tid":760052,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"入落銀行再撳500出嚟"},{"pid":"bd6c2022765b90fe80f516aa13b85fbd8c521e6c","tid":760052,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:46:42.000Z","msg":"叫啲鋪頭封柒左佢<br />\n有次去ok500入100都唔得"},{"pid":"a6cf8cb069b812abe77795abf9202263be6a9f49","tid":760052,"uid":103948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:50:04.000Z","msg":"港鐵客務收"},{"pid":"f2600e23aad2c9e39ff3827759ff3d03ce1f54d0","tid":760052,"uid":133545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T12:45:31.000Z","msg":"銀包無咩機會出現過一千蚊紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f047142b9bd66994dcc49b05d45bced6e1011963","tid":760052,"uid":108771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"之後取消港幣,統一用哂人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b664b58d12cf5a4c9a1ea99abe312d4ede40b532","tid":760052,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-